body:
Did anyone else feel

While they watched the Unicorn Store trailer that they just might be getting a very intimate glimpse into Brie Larson’s soul? I really feel like it’s her, her spirit, disguised as a film lol

She is such an introvert, yet here and now, she was ready and found a way to share a special part of herself to the world in a very creative way.

It’s not a bad thing, I just wanna know if anyone else feels this way lol like, you should feel honored when an introvert chooses to share something special of theirs with you, and that’s the vibe I got from the first watch lol
